Building a Stronger South Sudanese Community in France

Connecting, supporting, and celebrating our heritage since 2023

Who We Are

We are a nonprofit organization dedicated to supporting South Sudanese individuals and families in France through cultural preservation, education programs, and social initiatives that foster unity and belonging.
